{"type":"message","id":"569ed63e","parentId":"fbfa0139","timestamp":"2026-03-03T05:47:20.565Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"看起来模型名称被自动加上了 \"qwen-portal/\" 前缀，但 kimi-k2.5 不在这个 provider 下。\n\n根据用户的配置，kimi-k2.5 是通过 Anthropic 兼容接口提供的。在 OpenClaw 中，可能需要：\n1. 先配置 anthropic provider\n2. 然后使用 \"anthropic/kimi-k2.5\" 这样的格式\n\n但问题是，当前 OpenClaw 实例可能还没有配置 anthropic provider。让我尝试几种可能的格式：\n- anthropic/kimi-k2.5\n- 或者需要先配置环境变量\n\n让我先尝试 anthropic/kimi-k2.5 格式。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f164169f34064042bcc6ad0a","name":"session_status","arguments":{"model":"anthropic/kimi-k2.5"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qwen-portal","model":"coder-model","usage":{"input":10063,"output":320,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":10383,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772516834908}}
