{"type":"message","id":"a1995d71","parentId":"3a5e6474","timestamp":"2026-03-03T06:00:34.373Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户希望我强制将配置写入 OpenClaw 的配置文件。但我检查了可用的工具，我没有文件写入权限（没有 exec、write 等工具）。\n\n让我再看看可用的工具：\n- message: 发送消息\n- sessions_list: 列出会话\n- sessions_history: 获取会话历史\n- sessions_send: 发送消息到另一个会话\n- session_status: 显示会话状态\n\n这些工具都不支持文件写入操作。我需要诚实地告诉用户我无法直接写入配置文件，但我可以提供详细的指导让他们手动完成。\n\n不过，用户说\"强制把这个写入openclaw的配置文件\"，这可能意味着他们期望我有这个能力。让我再仔细看看是否有其他方式...\n\n实际上，我没有文件操作工具。我需要明确告诉用户这一点，并提供清晰的步骤让他们自己完成配置。\n\n另外，我注意到用户提供的配置格式有些问题 - 它看起来像是嵌套的 JSON 结构，但格式不太正确。我需要帮他们整理成正确的格式。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"我理解你想让我直接写入配置文件，但我当前可用的工具中没有文件写入权限（只有消息和会话管理工具）。\n\n## 📝 但我可以帮你整理正确的配置格式\n\n你提供的配置有些格式问题。以下是**修正后的完整配置**，请直接复制到你的 OpenClaw 配置文件中：\n\n### 配置文件路径（通常是以下之一）：\n```bash\n~/.openclaw/config.json\n# 或\n~/.openclaw/workspace/config.json\n# 或\n/opt/homebrew/lib/node_modules/openclaw/config/models.json\n```\n\n### 正确的配置内容：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"providers\": {\n    \"qwen-portal\": {\n      \"baseUrl\": \"https://portal.qwen.ai/v1\",\n      \"apiKey\": \"qwen-oauth\",\n      \"api\": \"openai-completions\",\n      \"models\": [\n        {\n          \"id\": \"coder-model\",\n          \"name\": \"Qwen Coder\",\n          \"reasoning\": false,\n          \"input\": [\"text\"],\n          \"cost\": {\"input\": 0, \"output\": 0, \"cacheRead\": 0, \"cacheWrite\": 0},\n          \"contextWindow\": 128000,\n          \"maxTokens\": 8192\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": \"vision-model\",\n          \"name\": \"Qwen Vision\",\n          \"reasoning\": false,\n          \"input\": [\"text\", \"image\"],\n          \"cost\": {\"input\": 0, \"output\": 0, \"cacheRead\": 0, \"cacheWrite\": 0},\n          \"contextWindow\": 128000,\n          \"maxTokens\": 8192\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    \"local-qwen\": {\n      \"baseUrl\": \"http://192.168.244.201:9091/api/model/f8e4cabe8bb0/v1\",\n      \"apiKey\": \"dkBRJ13pZgHg4HbRQyR5vttdlHEvuG5vlCiISzxQ0hSy5YkHzIgtJUOp9rNB5wWmhqWyOEVpDWe3AUEdLxDsoHx2Nlo6McSIPx50XYzxnf8gGIOaKI6wOcVDFj\",\n      \"api\": \"openai-completions\",\n      \"models\": [\n        {\n          \"id\": \"Qwen3-235B-A22B-Instruct-2507\",\n          \"name\": \"Qwen3 235B Instruct\",\n          \"reasoning\": false,\n          \"input\": [\"text\"],\n          \"cost\": {\"input\": 0, \"output\": 0, \"cacheRead\": 0, \"cacheWrite\": 0},\n          \"contextWindow\": 128000,\n          \"maxTokens\": 8192\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": \"Qwen3-VL-32B-Instruct\",\n          \"name\": \"Qwen3 VL 32B Instruct\",\n          \"api\": \"openai-completions\",\n          \"reasoning\": false,\n          \"input\": [\"text\", \"image\"],\n          \"cost\": {\"input\": 0, \"output\": 0},\n          \"contextWindow\": 32768,\n          \"maxTokens\": 8192\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    \"anthropic\": {\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"baseUrl\": \"https://coding.dashscope.aliyuncs.com/apps/anthropic\",\n      \"authToken\": \"sk-sp-7eeda6dd5dbf467ba8db9454b23d0acf\",\n      \"api\": \"anthropic-completions\",\n      \"models\": [\n        {\n          \"id\": \"kimi-k2.5\",\n          \"name\": \"Kimi K2.5\",\n          \"enabled\": true,\n          \"contextWindow\": 128000,\n          \"maxTokens\": 8192\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": \"qwen3.5-plus\",\n          \"name\": \"Qwen 3.5 Plus\",\n          \"enabled\": true\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": \"qwen3-max-2026-01-23\",\n          \"name\": \"Qwen3 Max\",\n          \"enabled\": true\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": \"MiniMax-M2.5\",\n          \"name\": \"MiniMax M2.5\",\n          \"enabled\": true\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": \"glm-5\",\n          \"name\": \"GLM 5\",\n          \"enabled\": true\n        }\n      ]\n    }\n  },\n  \"defaultProvider\": \"anthropic\",\n  \"defaultModel\": \"anthropic/kimi-k2.5\",\n  \"agents\": {\n    \"defaults\": {\n      \"model\": {\n        \"primary\": \"qwen-portal/vision-model\"\n      },\n      \"models\": {\n        \"local-qwen/Qwen3-235B-A22B-Instruct-2507\": {\"alias\": \"local\"},\n        \"qwen-portal/coder-model\": {\"alias\": \"qwen\"},\n        \"qwen-portal/vision-model\": {},\n        \"vl\": {\"alias\": \"vl\"},\n        \"vl-qwen/Qwen3-VL-32B-Instruct\": {\"alias\": \"vl\"},\n        \"anthropic/kimi-k2.5\": {\"alias\": \"kimi\"}\n      },\n      \"workspace\": \"/Users/lihzz/.openclaw/workspace\"\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n## 🔧 操作步骤：\n\n```bash\n# 1. 备份原配置\ncp ~/.openclaw/config.json ~/.openclaw/config.json.bak\n\n# 2. 编辑配置文件\ncode ~/.openclaw/config.json\n# 或\nnano ~/.openclaw/config.json\n\n# 3. 粘贴上面的配置，保存\n\n# 4. 重启 Gateway\nopenclaw gateway restart\n\n# 5. 验证\nopenclaw status\n```\n\n配置完成后告诉我，我会切换到 **kimi-k2.5** 进行测试！🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qwen-portal","model":"coder-model","usage":{"input":12507,"output":1846,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14353,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772517607606}}
