{"type":"message","id":"a6cad110","parentId":"13eee378","timestamp":"2026-03-03T06:03:22.939Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户提供了实际的配置文件路径 `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json`，现在我需要帮他们修改这个文件来添加 anthropic 提供商和 kimi-k2.5 模型。\n\n但是我仍然没有文件写入权限的工具。我需要用 sessions_send 来发送消息给控制 UI，告诉他们如何修改，或者看看是否有其他方式。\n\n让我检查一下可用的工具：\n- message: 发送消息到 channel\n- sessions_list: 列出会话\n- sessions_history: 获取会话历史\n- sessions_send: 发送消息到另一个会话\n- session_status: 显示会话状态\n\n我没有 exec 或文件操作工具。所以我需要指导用户手动修改文件。\n\n让我提供完整的修改后的配置内容，用户可以直接复制粘贴到 `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json`。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"找到了！配置文件在 `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json`。\n\n## 📝 请按以下步骤修改：\n\n### 1️⃣ 备份原文件\n```bash\ncp ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json.bak\n```\n\n### 2️⃣ 编辑配置文件\n```bash\ncode ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json\n# 或\nnano ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json\n```\n\n### 3️⃣ 替换 `models` 部分\n\n将原来的 `models` 部分替换为：\n\n```json\n\"models\": {\n  \"providers\": {\n    \"qwen-portal\": {\n      \"baseUrl\": \"https://portal.qwen.ai/v1\",\n      \"apiKey\": \"qwen-oauth\",\n      \"api\": \"openai-completions\",\n      \"models\": [\n        {\n          \"id\": \"coder-model\",\n          \"name\": \"Qwen Coder\",\n          \"reasoning\": false,\n          \"input\": [\"text\"],\n          \"cost\": {\"input\": 0, \"output\": 0, \"cacheRead\": 0, \"cacheWrite\": 0},\n          \"contextWindow\": 128000,\n          \"maxTokens\": 8192\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": \"vision-model\",\n          \"name\": \"Qwen Vision\",\n          \"reasoning\": false,\n          \"input\": [\"text\", \"image\"],\n          \"cost\": {\"input\": 0, \"output\": 0, \"cacheRead\": 0, \"cacheWrite\": 0},\n          \"contextWindow\": 128000,\n          \"maxTokens\": 8192\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    \"anthropic\": {\n      \"baseUrl\": \"https://coding.dashscope.aliyuncs.com/apps/anthropic\",\n      \"apiKey\": \"sk-sp-7eeda6dd5dbf467ba8db9454b23d0acf\",\n      \"api\": \"anthropic-completions\",\n      \"models\": [\n        {\n          \"id\": \"kimi-k2.5\",\n          \"name\": \"Kimi K2.5\",\n          \"reasoning\": false,\n          \"input\": [\"text\"],\n          \"cost\": {\"input\": 0, \"output\": 0, \"cacheRead\": 0, \"cacheWrite\": 0},\n          \"contextWindow\": 128000,\n          \"maxTokens\": 8192\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": \"qwen3.5-plus\",\n          \"name\": \"Qwen 3.5 Plus\",\n          \"reasoning\": false,\n          \"input\": [\"text\"],\n          \"cost\": {\"input\": 0, \"output\": 0, \"cacheRead\": 0, \"cacheWrite\": 0},\n          \"contextWindow\": 128000,\n          \"maxTokens\": 8192\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": \"qwen3-max-2026-01-23\",\n          \"name\": \"Qwen3 Max\",\n          \"reasoning\": false,\n          \"input\": [\"text\"],\n          \"cost\": {\"input\": 0, \"output\": 0, \"cacheRead\": 0, \"cacheWrite\": 0},\n          \"contextWindow\": 128000,\n          \"maxTokens\": 8192\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": \"MiniMax-M2.5\",\n          \"name\": \"MiniMax M2.5\",\n          \"reasoning\": false,\n          \"input\": [\"text\"],\n          \"cost\": {\"input\": 0, \"output\": 0, \"cacheRead\": 0, \"cacheWrite\": 0},\n          \"contextWindow\": 128000,\n          \"maxTokens\": 8192\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": \"glm-5\",\n          \"name\": \"GLM 5\",\n          \"reasoning\": true,\n          \"input\": [\"text\"],\n          \"cost\": {\"input\": 0, \"output\": 0, \"cacheRead\": 0, \"cacheWrite\": 0},\n          \"contextWindow\": 128000,\n          \"maxTokens\": 8192\n        }\n      ]\n    }\n  }\n},\n```\n\n### 4️⃣ 修改 `agents.defaults.model.primary`\n\n将：\n```json\n\"primary\": \"qwen-portal/coder-model\"\n```\n\n改为：\n```json\n\"primary\": \"anthropic/kimi-k2.5\"\n```\n\n### 5️⃣ 添加模型别名（可选）\n\n在 `agents.defaults.models` 中添加：\n```json\n\"anthropic/kimi-k2.5\": {\"alias\": \"kimi\"},\n\"anthropic/qwen3.5-plus\": {\"alias\": \"qwen35\"}\n```\n\n### 6️⃣ 保存并重启\n\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n### 7️⃣ 验证\n\n```bash\nopenclaw status\n```\n\n---\n\n修改完成后告诉我，我会切换到 **kimi-k2.5** 进行测试！🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qwen-portal","model":"coder-model","usage":{"input":14846,"output":1543,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16389,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772517781879}}
