lls\":\"auto\",\"restart\":true,\"ownerDisplay\":\"raw\"},\"session\":{\"dmScope\":\"per-channel-peer\"},\"gateway\":{\"port\":18789,\"mode\":\"local\",\"bind\":\"loopback\",\"auth\":{\"mode\":\"token\",\"token\":\"0bbfb0399fcf95bd2deefd552a2ece3f399e8bbae54920a2\"},\"tailscale\":{\"mode\":\"off\",\"resetOnExit\":false}},\"plugins\":{\"entries\":{\"qwen-portal-auth\":{\"enabled\":true}}}}\nEOF\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n---\n\n配置完成后告诉我，我会立即切换到 **kimi-k2.5** 进行测试！🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qwen-portal","model":"coder-model","usage":{"input":16138,"output":2918,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19056,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772517906809}}
{"type":"message","id":"62630fdb","parentId":"e09baf79","timestamp":"2026-03-03T06:07:55.043Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-03-03 14:07 GMT+8] 我怎么给你开通读写权限呢"}],"timestamp":1772518075041}}
{"type":"message","id":"2867ee26","parentId":"62630fdb","timestamp":"2026-03-03T06:08:08.125Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问如何给我开通读写权限。这是一个关于 OpenClaw 配置的问题。我需要告诉用户如何启用文件操作工具。\n\n在 OpenClaw 中，工具的可用性通常由配置控制。用户需要检查：\n1. tools 配置\n2. 是否有 bash/exec 工具可用\n3. 可能需要在配置中启用某些工具\n\n让我给用户提供清晰的指导。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好问题！在 OpenClaw 中，工具权限由配置文件控制。以下是开通读写权限的方法：\n\n## 🔧 启用文件操作工具\n\n### 方法一：修改 `openclaw.json` 的 `tools` 配置\n\n编辑 `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json`，找到 `tools` 部分：\n\n```json\n\"tools\": {\n  \"profile\": \"messaging\"\n}\n```\n\n改为：\n\n```json\n\"tools\": {\n  \"profile\": \"full\",\n  \"enabled\": [\"read\", \"write\", \"exec\", \"bash\"]\n}\n```\n\n或者添加具体的工具配置：\n\n```json\n\"tools\": {\n  \"profile\": \"custom\",\n  \"enabled\": [\"read\", \"write\", \"exec\", \"bash\", \"message\", \"sessions_list\", \"sessions_history\", \"sessions_send\", \"session_status\"],\n  \"bash\": {\n    \"enabled\": true,\n    \"pty\": true\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 方法二：使用 `openclaw config` 命令\n\n```bash\n# 查看当前工具配置\nopenclaw config show tools\n\n# 启用 bash 工具\nopenclaw config set tools.profile full\nopenclaw config set tools.enabled '[\"read\",\"write\",\"exec\",\"bash\"]'\n\n# 重启 gateway\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n### 方法三：检查技能配置\n\n有时工具权限在技能层面控制。检查：\n\n```bash\n# 查看可用技能\nopenclaw skills list\n\n# 如果有 coding-agent 技能，它需要 bash 工具\nopenclaw skills enable coding-agent\n```\n\n---\n\n## 📋 推荐配置\n\n在 `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json` 中设置：\n\n```json\n\"tools\": {\n  \"profile\": \"full\",\n  \"bash\": {\n    \"enabled\": true,\n    \"pty\": true,\n    \"allowedCommands\": [\"*\"]\n  }\n}\n```\n\n⚠️ **安全提示**：启用 `exec`/`bash` 后，我可以执行系统命令。请确保你信任这个环境。\n\n---\n\n配置完成后，重启 Gateway：\n\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n然后告诉我，我会：\n1. 直接修改配置文件添加 kimi-k2.5\n2. 重启服务\n3. 切换到新模型进行测试\n\n🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qwen-portal","model":"coder-model","usage":{"input":18657,"output":689,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19346,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772518075042}}
