{"type":"message","id":"0feb48fc","parentId":"75048a56","timestamp":"2026-03-03T06:18:56.117Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想查找可以编辑本地文件的 skills。我需要搜索可用的技能，看看哪些技能提供文件编辑功能。\n\n让我先列出可用的技能，然后查找与文件编辑相关的技能。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_9cdf3d8a5095419181d3e2b9","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","message":"## 🔍 查找文件编辑相关 Skills\n\n让我搜索可用的 skills：\n\n```bash\n# 列出所有已安装 skills\nopenclaw skills list\n\n# 搜索 clawhub 上的 skills\nopenclaw skills search file\nopenclaw skills search edit\nopenclaw skills search write\n```\n\n## 📝 常见的文件编辑 Skills\n\n根据 OpenClaw 生态，以下 skills 通常提供文件操作能力：\n\n### 1️⃣ **coding-agent**\n- 位置：`/opt/homebrew/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/coding-agent/SKILL.md`\n- 功能：代码编辑、文件创建/修改、PR 审查、重构\n- 需要：`bash` 工具（pty:true）\n- 启用：`openclaw skills enable coding-agent`\n\n### 2️⃣ **skill-creator**\n- 位置：`/opt/homebrew/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/skill-creator/SKILL.md`\n- 功能：创建/更新 AgentSkills，打包脚本和资产\n- 需要：文件读写权限\n- 启用：`openclaw skills enable skill-creator`\n\n### 3️⃣ **clawhub**\n- 位置：`/opt/homebrew/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/clawhub/SKILL.md`\n- 功能：搜索、安装、更新、发布 skills\n- 可以安装其他文件操作 skills\n- 启用：`openclaw skills enable clawhub`\n\n### 4️⃣ **healthcheck**\n- 位置：`/opt/homebrew/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/healthcheck/SKILL.md`\n- 功能：安全审计、配置检查\n- 需要读取配置文件权限\n- 启用：`openclaw skills enable healthcheck`\n\n## 🛠️ 启用步骤\n\n```bash\n# 1. 启用 coding-agent（最常用）\nopenclaw skills enable coding-agent\n\n# 2. 确认工具权限\nopenclaw config set tools.profile full\nopenclaw config set tools.enabled '[\"read\",\"write\",\"exec\",\"bash\"]'\n\n# 3. 重启\nopenclaw gateway restart\n\n# 4. 验证\nopenclaw skills list\n```\n\n## 📂 或者在 clawhub.com 搜索\n\n访问 https://clawhub.com 搜索：\n- `file-editor`\n- `config-edit`\n- `json-edit`\n- `text-editor`\n\n---\n\n**推荐先启用 `coding-agent`**，它是最通用的文件编辑技能，可以帮你完成 OpenClaw 配置文件修改！\n\n需要我帮你执行启用命令吗？🦞","target":"openclaw-tui"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qwen-portal","model":"coder-model","usage":{"input":19287,"output":713,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20000,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772518722726}}
{"type":"message","id":"de36e5dd","parentId":"0feb48fc","timestamp":"2026-03-03T06:18:56.169Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_9cdf3d8a5095419181d3e2b9","toolName":"message","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"status\": \"error\",\n  \"tool\": \"message\",\n  \"error\": \"Channel is required (no configured channels detected).\"\n}"}],"details":{"status":"error","tool":"message","error":"Channel is required (no configured channels detected)."},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772518736167}}
{"type":"message","id":"85e8cdb0","parentId":"de36e5dd","timestamp":"2026-03-03T06:19:07.223Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"消息工具需要 channel 参数，但当前没有配置的 channel。让我直接回复用户，告诉他们如何查找和启用文件编辑相关的 skills。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"## 🔍 查找文件编辑相关 Skills\n\n让我帮你查找可用的 skills：\n\n### 已安装的 Skills（本地路径）\n\n```bash\n# 列出所有已安装 skills\nls -la /opt/homebrew/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/\n```\n\n### 常见文件编辑 Skills\n\n根据 OpenClaw 标准技能库，以下 skills 提供文件操作能力：\n\n| Skill | 位置 | 功能 |\n|-------|------|------|\n| **coding-agent** | `/opt/homebrew/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/coding-agent/SKILL.md` | 代码编辑、文件创建/修改、PR 审查 |\n| **skill-creator** | `/opt/homebrew/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/skill-creator/SKILL.md` | 创建/更新 AgentSkills |\n| **clawhub** | `/opt/homebrew/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/clawhub/SKILL.md` | 搜索、安装、发布 skills |\n| **healthcheck** | `/opt/homebrew/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/healthcheck/SKILL.md` | 安全审计、配置检查 |\n\n### 启用步骤\n\n```bash\n# 1. 查看已安装 skills\nopenclaw skills list\n\n# 2. 启用 coding-agent（最通用）\nopenclaw skills enable coding-agent\n\n# 3. 配置工具权限\nopenclaw config set tools.profile full\nopenclaw config set tools.enabled '[\"read\",\"write\",\"exec\",\"bash\"]'\n\n# 4. 重启 Gateway\nopenclaw gateway restart\n\n# 5. 验证\nopenclaw status\n```\n\n### 在 ClawHub 搜索更多 Skills\n\n```bash\n# 搜索文件编辑相关 skills\nopenclaw skills search file\nopenclaw skills search edit\nopenclaw skills search config\n```\n\n或访问 https://clawhub.com 搜索：\n- `file-editor`\n- `json-edit`\n- `config-manager`\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 推荐方案\n\n**启用 `coding-agent`** 是最快的方式，它可以直接：\n1. 读取 `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json`\n2. 添加 anthropic 提供商配置\n3. 保存并重启 Gateway\n4. 切换到 kimi-k2.5 测试\n\n需要我帮你执行启用命令吗？🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qwen-portal","model":"coder-model","usage":{"input":20011,"output":578,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20589,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772518736169}}
