{"type":"message","id":"fd968e5c","parentId":"abb6a506","timestamp":"2026-03-03T06:19:23.890Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说需要我帮忙执行启用命令。但我之前已经确认过，我当前可用的工具只有 message、sessions_list、sessions_history、sessions_send、session_status，没有 exec 或 bash 工具来执行命令。\n\n我需要坦诚地告诉用户这个限制，并提供他们可以手动执行的命令。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的！但由于我当前没有 `exec`/`bash` 工具权限，我无法直接执行命令。\n\n## 📋 请在终端执行以下命令：\n\n### 1️⃣ 启用 coding-agent 技能\n\n```bash\nopenclaw skills enable coding-agent\n```\n\n### 2️⃣ 配置工具权限\n\n```bash\nopenclaw config set tools.profile full\nopenclaw config set tools.enabled '[\"read\",\"write\",\"exec\",\"bash\"]'\n```\n\n### 3️⃣ 重启 Gateway\n\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n### 4️⃣ 验证配置\n\n```bash\nopenclaw status\nopenclaw skills list\n```\n\n---\n\n## ✅ 完成后告诉我\n\n执行完以上命令后，告诉我，我会：\n\n1. 使用新的文件读写权限读取 `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json`\n2. 添加 anthropic 提供商和 kimi-k2.5 模型配置\n3. 保存配置文件\n4. 重启 Gateway\n5. 切换到 kimi-k2.5 进行测试\n\n🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qwen-portal","model":"coder-model","usage":{"input":20585,"output":366,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20951,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772518757841}}
