{"type":"message","id":"d0e6ea92","parentId":"abd3aa65","timestamp":"2026-03-03T06:24:48.749Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user has executed the command to enable tools. Now I should check if I have the new tools available. Let me try to use the session_status to see if there are any changes, or I should wait for the user to restart the gateway and then try to access files.\n\nActually, I need to be careful here - I don't actually have new tools available just because the user ran that command. The tools available to me are determined by the runtime configuration, not by commands the user runs in their terminal.\n\nLet me check what tools I actually have available by looking at my available functions again. I still only have:\n- message\n- sessions_list\n- sessions_history\n- sessions_send\n- session_status\n\nI don't have read/write/exec/bash tools. The user would need to restart the gateway and potentially re-authenticate or reload my session for new tools to become available.\n\nLet me guide them through the complete process and then have them restart everything.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的！你已执行了工具配置命令。现在需要完成以下步骤：\n\n## 🔄 完成配置流程\n\n### 1️⃣ 重启 Gateway（使工具配置生效）\n\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n### 2️⃣ 等待重启完成（约 5-10 秒）\n\n### 3️⃣ 验证工具已启用\n\n```bash\nopenclaw status\n```\n\n应该能看到 `tools: full` 或类似显示。\n\n### 4️⃣ 确认 coding-agent 已启用\n\n```bash\nopenclaw skills list\n```\n\n应该能看到 `coding-agent` 在已启用列表中。\n\n---\n\n## ✅ 完成后告诉我\n\n当以上步骤都完成后，告诉我 **\"配置完成\"**，我会：\n\n1. 📖 读取 `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json`\n2. ✏️ 添加 anthropic 提供商配置（kimi-k2.5 等模型）\n3. 💾 保存配置文件\n4. 🔄 重启 Gateway\n5. 🧪 切换到 kimi-k2.5 进行测试\n\n---\n\n**当前状态：** 等待你完成重启和验证 👀\n\n🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qwen-portal","model":"coder-model","usage":{"input":20941,"output":664,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21605,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772519077337}}
