{"type":"message","id":"f1613ce2","parentId":"ef58f19b","timestamp":"2026-03-03T07:16:13.363Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户确认了：\n1. 按照我提供的路径和方案执行\n2. 有本地的 Claude Code\n3. 有大模型的 API\n4. 只需要邮件通知（不需要 Telegram）\n\n我需要调整方案，把 Telegram 通知改成邮件通知，并提供完整的设置指南。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"## 🚀 好的！按我的方案实现，调整为邮件通知\n\n---\n\n## 📁 完整实现（邮件通知版）\n\n### 步骤 1: 创建目录结构\n\n```bash\nmkdir -p ~/openclaw-agents/{worktrees,scripts/{monitor,review,notify},tasks,logs}\n```\n\n---\n\n### 步骤 2: 创建配置文件 `~/openclaw-agents/config.json`\n\n```json\n{\n  \"agentSelection\": {\n    \"backend\": \"anthropic/kimi-k2.5\",\n    \"frontend\": \"anthropic/kimi-k2.5\",\n    \"ui-design\": \"anthropic/kimi-k2.5\",\n    \"default\": \"anthropic/kimi-k2.5\"\n  },\n  \"retryPolicy\": {\n    \"maxRetries\": 3,\n    \"backoffSeconds\": 300\n  },\n  \"contextSources\": [\n    \"~/obsidian/notes\",\n    \"~/obsidian/meetings\"\n  ],\n  \"notifyOnComplete\": true,\n  \"autoMerge\": false,\n  \"email\": {\n    \"enabled\": true,\n    \"smtpServer\": \"smtp.gmail.com\",\n    \"smtpPort\": 587,\n    \"username\": \"your-email@gmail.com\",\n    \"password\": \"your-app-password\",\n    \"from\": \"your-email@gmail.com\",\n    \"to\": \"your-email@gmail.com\"\n  },\n  \"github\": {\n    \"repo\": \"\",\n    \"requireReviews\": 3\n  },\n  \"claudeCode\": {\n    \"enabled\": true,\n    \"path\": \"~/.codex-agent/run-agent.sh\",\n    \"model\": \"claude-opus-4.5\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### 步骤 3: 创建启动脚本 `~/openclaw-agents/scripts/start-agent.sh`\n\n```bash\n#!/bin/bash\n# 启动一个 Agent 任务\n# 用法: ./start-agent.sh <task_id> <agent_type> <prompt> <worktree_name>\n\nset -e\n\nTASK_ID=$1\nAGENT_TYPE=${2:-default}\nPROMPT=$3\nWORKTREE_NAME=${4:-$TASK_ID}\n\nAGENTS_ROOT=~/openclaw-agents\nWORKTREES_DIR=$AGENTS_ROOT/worktrees\nTASKS_DIR=$AGENTS_ROOT/tasks\nLOGS_DIR=$AGENTS_ROOT/logs\nCONFIG_FILE=$AGENTS_ROOT/config.json\n\n# 创建目录\nmkdir -p \"$WORKTREES_DIR\" \"$TASKS_DIR\" \"$LOGS_DIR\"\n\n# 读取 Claude Code 配置\nCLAUDE_CODE_PATH=$(jq -r '.claudeCode.path' \"$CONFIG_FILE\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"$HOME/.codex-agent/run-agent.sh\")\nCLAUDE_MODEL=$(jq -r '.claudeCode.model' \"$CONFIG_FILE\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"claude-opus-4.5\")\n\n# 创建 worktree\necho \"🌳 Creating worktree: $WORKTREE_NAME\"\ncd ~/your-repo-path  # 替换为你的代码库路径\ngit worktree add \"$WORKTREES_DIR/$WORKTREE_NAME\" -b \"feat/$TASK_ID\" origin/main 2>/dev/null || {\n    echo \"Worktree exists, cleaning...\"\n    git worktree remove \"$WORKTREES_DIR/$WORKTREE_NAME\" 2>/dev/null || true\n    git worktree add \"$WORKTREES_DIR/$WORKTREE_NAME\" -b \"feat/$TASK_ID\" origin/main\n}\n\ncd \"$WORKTREES_DIR/$WORKTREE_NAME\"\n\n# 安装依赖\necho \"📦 Installing dependencies...\"\npnpm install --silent 2>/dev/null || npm install --silent 2>/dev/null || true\n\n# 启动 tmux 会话\nTMUX_SESSION=\"$AGENT_TYPE-$TASK_ID\"\nLOG_FILE=\"$LOGS_DIR/$TASK_ID.log\"\necho \"🤖 Starting agent in tmux: $TMUX_SESSION\"\n\ntmux new-session -d -s \"$TMUX_SESSION\" \\\n    -c \"$WORKTREES_DIR/$WORKTREE_NAME\"\n\n# 发送指令到会话（使用 Claude Code）\ntmux send-keys -t \"$TMUX_SESSION\" \"echo '=== Task: $TASK_ID ==='\" Enter\ntmux send-keys -t \"$TMUX_SESSION\" \"echo 'Started at: $(date)'\" Enter\ntmux send-keys -t \"$TMUX_SESSION\" \"echo 'Prompt: $PROMPT'\" Enter\ntmux send-keys -t \"$TMUX_SESSION\" \"\" Enter\ntmux send-keys -t \"$TMUX_SESSION\" \"# Running Claude Code...\" Enter\ntmux send-keys -t \"$TMUX_SESSION\" \"$CLAUDE_CODE_PATH --prompt \\\"$PROMPT\\\" --model $CLAUDE_MODEL 2>&1 | tee $LOG_FILE\" Enter\n\n# 记录任务\ncat > \"$TASKS_DIR/$TASK_ID.json\" << EOF\n{\n  \"id\": \"$TASK_ID\",\n  \"tmuxSession\": \"$TMUX_SESSION\",\n  \"agent\": \"$AGENT_TYPE\",\n  \"worktree\": \"$WORKTREE_NAME\",\n  \"branch\": \"feat/$TASK_ID\",\n  \"startedAt\": $(date +%s),\n  \"status\": \"running\",\n  \"prompt\": \"$PROMPT\",\n  \"retryCount\": 0\n}\nEOF\n\necho \"✅ Agent $TASK_ID started in tmux session $TMUX_SESSION\"\necho \"   Attach with: tmux attach -t $TMUX_SESSION\"\necho \"   Logs: $LOG_FILE\"\n```\n\n---\n\n### 步骤 4: 创建监控脚本 `~/openclaw-agents/scripts/monitor/loop.sh`\n\n```bash\n#!/bin/bash\n# 改进版 Ralph Loop - 监控所有 Agent 任务\n\nAGENTS_ROOT=~/openclaw-agents\nTASKS_DIR=$AGENTS_ROOT/tasks\nLOGS_DIR=$AGENTS_ROOT/logs\nCONFIG_FILE=$AGENTS_ROOT/config.json\n\n# 读取邮件配置\nEMAIL_ENABLED=$(jq -r '.email.enabled' \"$CONFIG_FILE\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"false\")\nSMTP_SERVER=$(jq -r '.email.smtpServer' \"$CONFIG_FILE\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"smtp.gmail.com\")\nSMTP_PORT=$(jq -r '.email.smtpPort' \"$CONFIG_FILE\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"587\")\nEMAIL_USER=$(jq -r '.email.username' \"$CONFIG_FILE\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"\")\nEMAIL_PASS=$(jq -r '.email.password' \"$CONFIG_FILE\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"\")\nEMAIL_FROM=$(jq -r '.email.from' \"$CONFIG_FILE\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"\")\nEMAIL_TO=$(jq -r '.email.to' \"$CONFIG_FILE\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"\")\n\n# 发送邮件函数\nsend_email() {\n    local subject=\"$1\"\n    local body=\"$2\"\n    \n    if [ \"$EMAIL_ENABLED\" != \"true\" ] || [ -z \"$EMAIL_USER\" ]; then\n        echo \"[EMAIL SKIP] $subject\"\n        return\n    fi\n    \n    # 使用 mail 命令或 sendmail\n    if command -v mail &> /dev/null; then\n        echo \"$body\" | mail -s \"$subject\" -r \"$EMAIL_FROM\" -S smtp=\"$SMTP_SERVER:$SMTP_PORT\" \\\n            -S smtp-auth=login -S smtp-auth-user=\"$EMAIL_USER\" -S smtp-auth-password=\"$EMAIL_PASS\" \\\n            \"$EMAIL_TO\"\n    elif command -v sendmail &> /dev/null; then\n        {\n            echo \"From: $EMAIL_FROM\"\n            echo \"To: $EMAIL_TO\"\n            echo \"Subject: $subject\"\n            echo \"\"\n            echo \"$body\"\n        } | sendmail -t\n    else\n        # 使用 Python 发送\n        python3 << PYEOF\nimport smtplib\nfrom email.mime.text import MIMEText\n\nmsg = MIMEText('''$body''')\nmsg['Subject'] = '$subject'\nmsg['From'] = '$EMAIL_FROM'\nmsg['To'] = '$EMAIL_TO'\n\ntry:\n    server = smtplib.SMTP('$SMTP_SERVER', $SMTP_PORT)\n    server.starttls()\n    server.login('$EMAIL_USER', '$EMAIL_PASS')\n    server.send_message(msg)\n    server.quit()\n    print(\"Email sent: $subject\")\nexcept Exception as e:\n    print(f\"Email failed: {e}\")\nPYEOF\n    fi\n    \n    echo \"[EMAIL SENT] $subject\"\n}\n\n# 主监控循环\nfor task_file in \"$TASKS_DIR\"/*.json; do\n    [ -f \"$task_file\" ] || continue\n    \n    TASK_ID=$(jq -r '.id' \"$task_file\" 2>/dev/null)\n    TMUX_SESSION=$(jq -r '.tmuxSession' \"$task_file\" 2>/dev/null)\n    STATUS=$(jq -r '.status' \"$task_file\" 2>/dev/null)\n    BRANCH=$(jq -r '.branch' \"$task_file\" 2>/dev/null)\n    PROMPT=$(jq -r '.prompt' \"$task_file\" 2>/dev/null)\n    \n    [ -z \"$TASK_ID\" ] && continue\n    \n    echo \"[$(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')] Checking task: $TASK_ID (status: $STATUS)\"\n    \n    # 检查 tmux 会话是否存活\n    if ! tmux has-session -t \"$TMUX_SESSION\" 2>/dev/null; then\n        echo \"[$TASK_ID] Session ended, checking results...\"\n        \n        LOG_FILE=\"$LOGS_DIR/$TASK_ID.log\"\n        \n        # 检查是否有 PR 创建\n        if [ -f \"$LOG_FILE\" ]; then\n            PR_LOG=$(grep -i \"Created PR\\|Pull request\\|github.com.*/pull\" \"$LOG_FILE\" 2>/dev/null | tail -1 || echo \"\")\n        else\n            PR_LOG=\"\"\n        fi\n        \n        if [ -n \"$PR_LOG\" ]; then\n            PR_URL=$(echo \"$PR_LOG\" | grep -oE 'https://github.com[^ >]+' | head -1)\n            \n            if [ -n \"$PR_URL\" ]; then\n                # 检查 CI 状态 (需要 gh CLI)\n                if command -v gh &> /dev/null && [ -n \"$PR_URL\" ]; then\n                    CI_STATUS=$(gh pr view \"$PR_URL\" --json checkSuites --jq '.checkSuites[0].status' 2>/dev/null || echo \"UNKNOWN\")\n                    \n                    if [ \"$CI_STATUS\" = \"COMPLETED\" ] || [ \"$CI_STATUS\" = \"UNKNOWN\" ]; then\n                        send_email \"🎉 PR Ready: $TASK_ID\" \"PR #$TASK_ID is ready for review.\\n\\nURL: $PR_URL\\nTask: $PROMPT\"\n                        \n                        jq '.status = \"ready_review\" | .completedAt = '\"$(date +%s)\"'' \"$task_file\" > \"$task_file.tmp\"\n                        mv \"$task_file.tmp\" \"$task_file\"\n                    fi\n                else\n                    send_email \"🎉 PR Ready: $TASK_ID\" \"PR #$TASK_ID is ready for review.\\n\\nURL: $PR_URL\\nTask: $PROMPT\"\n                    \n                    jq '.status = \"ready_review\" | .completedAt = '\"$(date +%s)\"'' \"$task_file\" > \"$task_file.tmp\"\n                    mv \"$task_file.tmp\" \"$task_file\"\n                fi\n            else\n                # 有日志但没有 PR，可能是失败了\n                send_email \"⚠️ Task Completed: $TASK_ID\" \"Task #$TASK_ID completed but no PR created.\\n\\nPrompt: $PROMPT\\nCheck logs: $LOG_FILE\"\n                jq '.status = \"completed_no_pr\" | .completedAt = '\"$(date +%s)\"'' \"$task_file\" > \"$task_file.tmp\"\n                mv \"$task_file.tmp\" \"$task_file\"\n            fi\n        else\n            # 任务失败，检查重试\n            RETRY_COUNT=$(jq -r '.retryCount // 0' \"$task_file\")\n            MAX_RETRIES=$(jq -r '.retryPolicy.maxRetries' \"$CONFIG_FILE\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"3\")\n            \n            if [ \"$RETRY_COUNT\" -lt \"$MAX_RETRIES\" ]; then\n                echo \"[$TASK_ID] Retrying... ($RETRY_COUNT/$MAX_RETRIES)\"\n                send_email \"🔄 Retrying: $TASK_ID\" \"Task #$TASK_ID failed, retrying ($RETRY_COUNT/$MAX_RETRIES).\\n\\nPrompt: $PROMPT\"\n                \n                jq '.retryCount = (.retryCount // 0) + 1 | .status = \"retrying\"' \"$task_file\" > \"$task_file.tmp\"\n                mv \"$task_file.tmp\" \"$task_file\"\n                \n                # 重新启动 Agent\n                WORKTREE=$(jq -r '.worktree' \"$task_file\")\n                cd ~/openclaw-agents/scripts\n                ./start-agent.sh \"$TASK_ID\" \"default\" \"$PROMPT\" \"$WORKTREE\"\n            else\n                send_email \"❌ Task Failed: $TASK_ID\" \"Task #$TASK_ID failed after $MAX_RETRIES retries.\\n\\nPrompt: $PROMPT\\nPlease check manually.\"\n                jq '.status = \"failed\" | .failedAt = '\"$(date +%s)\"'' \"$task_file\" > \"$task_file.tmp\"\n                mv \"$task_file.tmp\" \"$task_file\"\n            fi\n        fi\n    fi\ndone\n\necho \"[$(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')] Monitor loop completed\"\n```\n\n---\n\n### 步骤 5: 创建邮件通知脚本 `~/openclaw-agents/scripts/notify/email.sh`\n\n```bash\n#!/bin/bash\n# 邮件通知脚本\n# 用法: ./email.sh <subject> <body>\n\nSUBJECT=$1\nBODY=$2\n\nCONFIG_FILE=~/openclaw-agents/config.json\n\nEMAIL_ENABLED=$(jq -r '.email.enabled' \"$CONFIG_FILE\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"false\")\nSMTP_SERVER=$(jq -r '.email.smtpServer' \"$CONFIG_FILE\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"smtp.gmail.com\")\nSMTP_PORT=$(jq -r '.email.smtpPort' \"$CONFIG_FILE\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"587\")\nEMAIL_USER=$(jq -r '.email.username' \"$CONFIG_FILE\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"\")\nEMAIL_PASS=$(jq -r '.email.password' \"$CONFIG_FILE\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"\")\nEMAIL_FROM=$(jq -r '.email.from' \"$CONFIG_FILE\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"\")\nEMAIL_TO=$(jq -r '.email.to' \"$CONFIG_FILE\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"\")\n\nif [ \"$EMAIL_ENABLED\" != \"true\" ] || [ -z \"$EMAIL_USER\" ]; then\n    echo \"Email not configured, skipping notification\"\n    exit 0\nfi\n\n# 使用 Python 发送邮件\npython3 << PYEOF\nimport smtplib\nfrom email.mime.text import MIMEText\n\nmsg = MIMEText('''$BODY''')\nmsg['Subject'] = '$SUBJECT'\nmsg['From'] = '$EMAIL_FROM'\nmsg['To'] = '$EMAIL_TO'\n\ntry:\n    server = smtplib.SMTP('$SMTP_SERVER', $SMTP_PORT)\n    server.starttls()\n    server.login('$EMAIL_USER', '$EMAIL_PASS')\n    server.send_message(msg)\n    server.quit()\n    print(\"✅ Email sent: $SUBJECT\")\nexcept Exception as e:\n    print(f\"❌ Email failed: {e}\")\n    exit(1)\nPYEOF\n```\n\n---\n\n### 步骤 6: 创建 GitHub Actions 工作流 `.github/workflows/auto-review.yml`\n\n```yaml\nname: Auto Code Review\n\non:\n  pull_request:\n    types: [opened, synchronize, reopened]\n\njobs:\n  ci-checks:\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    steps:\n      - uses: actions/checkout@v4\n      \n      - name: Setup Node.js\n        uses: actions/setup-node@v4\n        with:\n          node-version: '20'\n          \n      - name: Install dependencies\n        run: pnpm install --frozen-lockfile || npm ci\n        \n      - name: Lint\n        run: pnpm lint || npm run lint\n        continue-on-error: true\n        \n      - name: Type Check\n        run: pnpm typecheck || npm run typecheck\n        continue-on-error: true\n        \n      - name: Test\n        run: pnpm test || npm test\n        continue-on-error: true\n\n  notify-complete:\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    needs: ci-checks\n    if: always()\n    steps:\n      - name: Notify PR Status\n        uses: actions/github-script@v7\n        with:\n          script: |\n            const status = '${{ needs.ci-checks.result }}';\n            const prNumber = context.payload.pull_request.number;\n            console.log(`PR #${prNumber} CI status: ${status}`);\n```\n\n---\n\n### 步骤 7: 设置 Cron 监控\n\n```bash\n# 编辑 crontab\ncrontab -e\n\n# 添加以下行（每 10 分钟检查一次）\n*/10 * * * * ~/openclaw-agents/scripts/monitor/loop.sh >> ~/openclaw-agents/logs/monitor.log 2>&1\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🔧 完整设置命令\n\n```bash\n# ===== 1. 创建目录 =====\nmkdir -p ~/openclaw-agents/{worktrees,scripts/{monitor,review,notify},tasks,logs}\n\n# ===== 2. 创建配置文件 =====\ncat > ~/openclaw-agents/config.json << 'EOF'\n{\n  \"agentSelection\": {\n    \"backend\": \"anthropic/kimi-k2.5\",\n    \"frontend\": \"anthropic/kimi-k2.5\",\n    \"ui-design\": \"anthropic/kimi-k2.5\",\n    \"default\": \"anthropic/kimi-k2.5\"\n  },\n  \"retryPolicy\": {\n    \"maxRetries\": 3,\n    \"backoffSeconds\": 300\n  },\n  \"email\": {\n    \"enabled\": true,\n    \"smtpServer\": \"smtp.gmail.com\",\n    \"smtpPort\": 587,\n    \"username\": \"YOUR_EMAIL@gmail.com\",\n    \"password\": \"YOUR_APP_PASSWORD\",\n    \"from\": \"YOUR_EMAIL@gmail.com\",\n    \"to\": \"YOUR_EMAIL@gmail.com\"\n  },\n  \"claudeCode\": {\n    \"enabled\": true,\n    \"path\": \"~/.codex-agent/run-agent.sh\",\n    \"model\": \"claude-opus-4.5\"\n  }\n}\nEOF\n\n# ===== 3. 创建启动脚本 =====\n# (复制上面的 start-agent.sh 内容)\n\n# ===== 4. 创建监控脚本 =====\n# (复制上面的 loop.sh 内容)\n\n# ===== 5. 创建邮件脚本 =====\n# (复制上面的 email.sh 内容)\n\n# ===== 6. 设置执行权限 =====\nchmod +x ~/openclaw-agents/scripts/*.sh\nchmod +x ~/openclaw-agents/scripts/*/*.sh\n\n# ===== 7. 配置 Cron =====\n(crontab -l 2>/dev/null; echo \"*/10 * * * * ~/openclaw-agents/scripts/monitor/loop.sh >> ~/openclaw-agents/logs/monitor.log 2>&1\") | crontab -\n\n# ===== 8. 验证 =====\ncrontab -l\nls -la ~/openclaw-agents/\n```\n\n---\n\n## 📧 邮件配置说明\n\n### Gmail 用户：\n1. 启用两步验证\n2. 生成应用专用密码：https://myaccount.google.com/apppasswords\n3. 在 `config.json` 中填写：\n   - `username`: 你的 Gmail 地址\n   - `password`: 应用专用密码（不是登录密码）\n\n### 其他邮箱：\n| 邮箱 | SMTP Server | Port |\n|------|-------------|------|\n| Gmail | smtp.gmail.com | 587 |\n| Outlook | smtp.office365.com | 587 |\n| QQ 邮箱 | smtp.qq.com | 587 |\n| 163 邮箱 | smtp.163.com | 587 |\n\n---\n\n## ✅ 验证清单\n\n```bash\n# 1. 检查目录结构\nls -la ~/openclaw-agents/\n\n# 2. 检查配置文件\ncat ~/openclaw-agents/config.json\n\n# 3. 测试邮件发送\n~/openclaw-agents/scripts/notify/email.sh \"Test Subject\" \"Test Body\"\n\n# 4. 测试 Agent 启动（替换为你的代码库路径）\ncd ~/openclaw-agents/scripts\n./start-agent.sh test-task default \"Hello World\" test-worktree\n\n# 5. 检查 tmux\ntmux list-sessions\n\n# 6. 检查任务记录\ncat ~/openclaw-agents/tasks/test-task.json\n\n# 7. 测试监控\n~/openclaw-agents/scripts/monitor/loop.sh\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 下一步\n\n请执行以下命令开始：\n\n```bash\n# 1. 创建目录\nmkdir -p ~/openclaw-agents/{worktrees,scripts/{monitor,review,notify},tasks,logs}\n\n# 2. 告诉我你的代码库路径（替换 ~/your-repo-path）\n# 3. 告诉我你的邮箱地址（用于配置邮件通知）\n```\n\n完成后告诉我，我会帮你验证配置！🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qwen-portal","model":"coder-model","usage":{"input":33550,"output":4917,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38467,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772521976883}}
