{"type":"message","id":"54cb8f4f","parentId":"a7b23fea","timestamp":"2026-03-03T07:54:13.137Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to run `openclaw status`, but I don't have exec/bash tool permissions to execute commands. I need to remind them that they need to run this command themselves in their terminal and share the output with me.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"## ⚠️ 我无法执行命令\n\n我没有 `exec`/`bash` 工具权限，无法在终端执行命令。\n\n---\n\n## 📋 请你在终端执行\n\n```bash\nopenclaw status\n```\n\n然后把输出结果粘贴给我。\n\n---\n\n## 🔧 如果你想要我直接执行命令\n\n你需要先给我开通工具权限。在 `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json` 中配置：\n\n```json\n\"tools\": {\n  \"profile\": \"full\",\n  \"enabled\": [\"read\", \"write\", \"exec\", \"bash\"]\n}\n```\n\n然后重启 Gateway：\n\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n---\n\n请执行 `openclaw status` 并粘贴输出，我会帮你分析当前状态！🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qwen-portal","model":"coder-model","usage":{"input":43050,"output":275,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43325,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772524422324}}
