{"type":"message","id":"18b5a5a5","parentId":"cc68e7ae","timestamp":"2026-03-03T08:21:14.643Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想让我查看路径下的文件，但我没有文件读取权限。我需要再次说明这个限制，并请用户自己执行命令查看。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"## ⚠️ 我当前没有文件读取权限\n\n我可用的工具只有：\n- `message` - 发送消息\n- `sessions_list` - 列出会话\n- `sessions_history` - 获取历史\n- `sessions_send` - 跨会话发消息\n- `session_status` - 查看状态\n\n**没有** `read`/`exec`/`bash` 工具权限，无法查看文件系统。\n\n---\n\n## 📋 请你在终端执行以下命令\n\n```bash\n# 查看工作区文件\nls -la /Users/lihzz/.openclaw/workspace/\n\n# 查看 OpenClaw 配置\nls -la ~/.openclaw/\n\n# 查看 Agent 系统目录\nls -la ~/openclaw-agents/\n\n# 查看代码库\nls -la /Users/lihzz/openclawCode/\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 或者执行这个一键命令\n\n```bash\necho \"=== 工作区 ===\" && ls -la /Users/lihzz/.openclaw/workspace/ && echo \"\" && echo \"=== OpenClaw 配置 ===\" && ls -la ~/.openclaw/ && echo \"\" && echo \"=== Agent 系统 ===\" && ls -la ~/openclaw-agents/ 2>/dev/null || echo \"未找到\" && echo \"\" && echo \"=== 代码库 ===\" && ls -la /Users/lihzz/openclawCode/\n```\n\n---\n\n## ✅ 把输出粘贴给我\n\n执行后把结果粘贴给我，我会帮你分析：\n1. 哪些文件已存在\n2. 哪些配置需要完成\n3. 下一步该做什么\n\n🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qwen-portal","model":"coder-model","usage":{"input":43310,"output":422,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43732,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772526051019}}
